page.title: 09A TYPICAL DAY
page.content: I get up at about 8:15am and get dressed then I brush my teeth and wash my face and hands.After that I go down stairs and get my games kit ready.I have breakfast at half past eight. After breakfast I feed the hens and ducks. Then I go to school.On Monday morning we have Mrs Taplin.At 10:30 we have play time for 15 minutes. After play time we do maths. I enjoy maths especially fractions.At 12:00 we go for sandwiches. I've finished my lunch by 12:20.I play in the play ground till 1:00. Then we go into class and work with Mr Smith till 2:15. Then we go to play.At playtime I play football on the field. After play we would have Mr Smith.At 3:15 we go home.When I get home I feed the hens and ducks after that I go out on my bike until 6:00. At 6:00 I have supper.After supper I go out until 9:00.
